items.title: Our Mission
items.summary: Our mission is to establish circular economy. We believe that the world we live in is dying and that we need to protect it. To help us, we encourage you as the consumers to give us your soakers if they need repairing. We also encourage…
items.content_html:
Our mission is to establish circular economy. We believe that the world we live in is dying and that we need to protect it. To help us, we encourage you as the consumers to give us your soakers if they need repairing. We also encourage you to give us old sheets of fabric with a minimum dimension of 50cm x 40cm and we can make it into a pair of soakers.

items.content_html:
We are a family of four. Tee started skating when she was three and was having fun. When she saw her older cousin, Tee was determined to be a figure skater. Five years later, she is now going to competitions. Tee and her family love to make ice tea and our business was inspired by her ice skating and the family's favourite drink, ice tea.
